---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy policy for WooPlugin products and services."
>
  <Header />
  <main class="pt-32 pb-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-text mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-text-muted mb-8">Last updated: January 2026</p>

      <div class="prose prose-lg text-text-muted space-y-8">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">Overview</h2>
          <p>
            WooPlugin ("we", "our", or "us") respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal data.
            This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, and protect information when you use our website and plugins.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">Information We Collect</h2>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-2 mt-6">Website</h3>
          <p>When you visit wooplugin.pro, we may collect:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mt-2">
            <li>Contact form submissions (name, email, message)</li>
            <li>Basic analytics data (page views, referrer, browser type, country)</li>
            <li>Purchase information (name, email, billing address) when you buy Pro</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-2 mt-6">Free Plugin</h3>
          <p>
            Our free WordPress plugin does not collect or transmit any personal data to our servers.
            All product data stays on your WordPress installation. The plugin generates feed files
            locally on your server.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-2 mt-6">Pro Plugin</h3>
          <p>When using the Pro plugin, the following data may be transmitted to our servers:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mt-2">
            <li>License key validation (license key, site URL)</li>
            <li>Update checks (plugin version, WordPress version, site URL)</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-4">
            We do <strong>not</strong> collect: your product data, customer information, API keys,
            or any sensitive store data. Your feed files are generated and stored locally on your server.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">How We Use Information</h2>
          <p>We use collected information to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mt-2">
            <li>Respond to your inquiries and support requests</li>
            <li>Improve our website and plugins</li>
            <li>Send important updates about our products (only if you opt in)</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">Cookies</h2>
          <p>Our website uses cookies to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mt-2">
            <li>Remember your preferences</li>
            <li>Understand how you use our website (analytics)</li>
            <li>Process purchases (essential cookies)</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-4">
            You can control cookies through your browser settings. Disabling cookies may affect
            some website functionality.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">Data Storage and Retention</h2>
          <p>We retain your data as follows:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mt-2">
            <li><strong>Contact form submissions:</strong> Deleted after 2 years or upon request</li>
            <li><strong>Purchase records:</strong> Retained for 7 years for tax/legal compliance</li>
            <li><strong>License data:</strong> Retained while your license is active, plus 1 year after expiration</li>
            <li><strong>Analytics data:</strong> Aggregated and anonymized after 26 months</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-4">
            We do not sell or share your personal information with third parties for marketing purposes.
            We may share data with service providers who help us operate our business, or as required by law.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">Third-Party Services</h2>
          <p>We use the following third-party services:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mt-2">
            <li><strong>Payment processing:</strong> Your payment is processed securely by our payment provider. We do not store your credit card details on our servers.</li>
            <li><strong>Analytics:</strong> We use privacy-focused analytics to understand website usage.</li>
            <li><strong>Email:</strong> We use email services to send transactional emails (purchase confirmations, license keys).</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-2 mt-6">Plugin Integrations</h3>
          <p>Our plugins generate feeds for third-party platforms:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mt-2">
            <li>Google Merchant Center</li>
            <li>Facebook/Meta Catalog (Pro)</li>
            <li>Pinterest, TikTok, Bing, Snapchat (Pro)</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-4">
            Feed files are generated and stored on your server. You control when and how this data
            is shared with these platforms by submitting the feed URL. We do not transmit your
            product data to our servers.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">Security</h2>
          <p>
            We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your personal data,
            including encryption in transit (HTTPS), secure servers, and access controls. However, no
            method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">Your Rights</h2>
          <p>You have the right to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mt-2">
            <li>Request access to your personal data</li>
            <li>Request correction or deletion of your data</li>
            <li>Request data portability (receive your data in a structured format)</li>
            <li>Object to processing of your data</li>
            <li>Withdraw consent at any time</li>
            <li>Opt out of marketing communications</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-4">
            To exercise these rights, contact us at the email below. We will respond within 30 days.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">GDPR Compliance</h2>
          <p>
            If you are located in the European Economic Area (EEA), we process your personal data
            based on the following legal bases:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mt-2">
            <li><strong>Contract:</strong> To fulfill our obligations when you purchase a license</li>
            <li><strong>Legitimate interest:</strong> To improve our products and prevent fraud</li>
            <li><strong>Consent:</strong> For marketing communications (you can withdraw anytime)</li>
            <li><strong>Legal obligation:</strong> To comply with tax and accounting requirements</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">International Data Transfers</h2>
          <p>
            Your data may be processed in countries outside your residence. We ensure appropriate
            safeguards are in place, such as standard contractual clauses, to protect your data
            in accordance with applicable privacy laws.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">Children's Privacy</h2>
          <p>
            Our services are not directed to children under 16. We do not knowingly collect personal
            data from children. If we become aware that we have collected data from a child, we will
            delete it promptly.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p>
            We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify you of significant
            changes by posting a notice on our website or sending you an email. Your continued use
            of our services after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">Contact</h2>
          <p>
            For privacy-related questions, please contact us through the
            <a href="/#contact" class="text-primary hover:text-primary-dark">contact form</a>
            on our website.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
